snippet.title: Chris Washington | Have A Word Podcast #116
snippet.description:
Adam and Dan are doing solo stand-up tours next year, get tickets below: 
Dan Nightingale Smasher | http://dannightingale.com 
Adam Rowe Imperious | https://www.adamrowe.co.uk/shows


As Adam said, don't miss out on all of our extra content, we've got one of the best value Patreons in the game. An extra 90+ minute episode every week plus loads of bonus content such as the now infamous Lockdown Lock-ins and Sensei Carl's Big Fat Quiz! What are you waiting for? Sign up now at https://patreon.com/haveawordpod​.

Thanks to this week's sponsors:

SupremeCBD | https://supremecbd.uk
30% off with code: WORD

Manscaped | https://manscaped.com
20% off with the promo code: WORD

Beer52 | https://beer52.com/word
A free case of eight beers, a magazine and a tasty snack for all our listeners.

Become one of the lids:
https://patreon.com/haveawordpod

Tickets & merch:
https://haveawordpod.com

Follow the podcast, our hosts and our guest on social media:
https://instagram.com/haveawordpod
https://twitter.com/haveawordpod
https://facebook.com/haveawordpod

Adam Rowe
https://instagram.com/adamrowecomedian
https://twitter.com/adamrowecomedy
https://facebook.com/adamrowecomedian

Dan Nightingale
https://instagram.com/danhasapodcast
https://twitter.com/danhasapodcast
https://facebook.com/danhasapodcast

ADAM ROWE and DAN NIGHTINGALE are two award winning comedians from Liverpool & Preston, respectively. They are two of the UK's most highly regarded stand-ups and have both performed all over the world.
